                    <span>I love books and movies that make me believe in magic the way I did as a child.  Finding Neverland reminds us all, that if you just see with different eyes, that magic exists.  This movie will make you smile, laugh, and cry.  Suspend your disbelief for a while and take a trip back to your childhood.</span>
                  
